<quickviewtext name="Quick View">
<![CDATA[
<p>The <span class="title-main">Mathematical &amp; Scientific Computation </span>major is the ideal choice for students who are interested in the interplay between mathematical theory and modern computational tools for applications. Students build a foundation enabling them to model or analyze complicated systems or problems such as earthquakes, economic models, or biological systems.</p>
